description:
Steve and Johnny examine Daniel 8 about the ram, the goat, and the self-exalting horn who attacks God’s sanctuary. For how long? “Until 2300 days, then shall the sanctuary be cleansed.” Daniel 8:14. Discover prophetic facts few today understand.
